                                <img class="d-block mx-auto mb-4" src="/Resource/logo4.png" alt="Logo" width="100" height="100">

                <h1 class="display-4 fw-bold text-white">Learn to Code</h1>
                <h4 class="fw-light text-white opacity-50">Build Projects, Master Skills</h4>
                <div class="col-lg-6 mx-auto">
                    <p class="lead my-4 text-white opacity-75">
                        Start your coding journey today. Build real-world projects and sharpen your programming skills.
                    </p>
                    <div class="d-grid gap-2 d-sm-flex justify-content-sm-center">
                        <a href="#" class="btn btn-lg px-4 fw-bold rounded-pill newfonts" style="background-color: white; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 18px;">Explore Now</a>
