                    </div>
                </div>
            </main>
            
            <section class="features py-5">
                <div class="container">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-lg-4">
                            <h2 class="fw-bold text-white">Python</h2>
                            <img src="/Resource/py.png" alt="Python" class="img-fluid mb-3" style="height: 125px;">
                            <p class="text-white opacity-75">Learn Python, a powerful language used for web development, data analysis, artificial intelligence, and more. Python's simple syntax and readability make it an excellent choice for beginners and professionals alike. Dive into Python's extensive libraries and frameworks to build robust applications and automate tasks efficiently.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-lg-4">
                            <h2 class="fw-bold text-white">CSS</h2>
                            <img src="/Resource/cs.png" alt="CSS" class="img-fluid mb-3" style="height: 100px;">
                            <p class="text-white opacity-75">Master CSS to create visually appealing and responsive web designs. CSS (Cascading Style Sheets) is essential for styling HTML elements and controlling the layout of web pages. Learn how to use CSS Grid, Flexbox, animations, and media queries to build modern, responsive designs that look great on any device.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-lg-4">
                            <h2 class="fw-bold text-white">JavaScript</h2>
                            <img src="/Resource/js.png" alt="JavaScript" class="img-fluid mb-3" style="height: 100px;">
                            <p class="text-white opacity-75">Understand JavaScript to build dynamic and interactive web applications. JavaScript is a versatile programming language that runs in the browser and on the server (Node.js). Learn how to manipulate the DOM, handle events, and create interactive features like sliders, forms, and single-page applications. Explore frameworks and libraries like React, Angular, and Vue.js to enhance your development skills.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
            
            <section class="python py-5 bg-light">
                <div class="container">
                    <img src="/Resource/a.jpeg" alt="Python" class="img-fluid mb-3 d-block mx-auto">
                    <p class="text-dark opacity-75">Learn Python, a powerful language used for web development, data analysis, artificial intelligence, and more. Python's simple syntax and readability make it an excellent choice for beginners and professionals alike. Dive into Python's extensive libraries and frameworks to build robust applications and automate tasks efficiently.</p>
                    <p class="text-dark opacity-75">Learn Python, a powerful language used for web development, data analysis, artificial intelligence, and more.</p>
                </div>
            </section>
            
            <section class="css py-5 bg-secondary">
                <div class="container">
                    <img src="/Resource/b.jpg" alt="CSS" class="img-fluid mb-3 d-block mx-auto">
                    <p class="text-white opacity-75">Master CSS to create visually appealing and responsive web designs. CSS (Cascading Style Sheets) is essential for styling HTML elements and controlling the layout of web pages. Learn how to use CSS Grid, Flexbox, animations, and media queries to build modern, responsive designs that look great on any device.</p>
                    <p class="text-white opacity-75">Master CSS to create visually appealing and responsive web designs.</p>
                </div>
            </section>
            
            <section class="javascript py-5 bg-light">
                <div class="container">
                    <img src="/Resource/c.jpg" alt="JavaScript" class="img-fluid mb-3 d-block mx-auto">
                    <p class="text-dark opacity-75">Understand JavaScript to build dynamic and interactive web applications. JavaScript is a versatile programming language that runs in the browser and on the server (Node.js). Learn how to manipulate the DOM, handle events, and create interactive features like sliders, forms, and single-page applications. Explore frameworks and libraries like React, Angular, and Vue.js to enhance your development skills.</p>
                    <p class="text-dark opacity-75">Understand JavaScript to build dynamic and interactive web applications.</p>
                </div>
            </section>
            
            <section class="testimonials py-5 bg-dark">
                <div class="container">
                    <h2 class="fw-bold text-white text-center">What Our Users Say</h2>
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-lg-4">
                            <blockquote class="blockquote text-white">
                                <p>"This platform has transformed my coding skills!"</p>
                                <footer class="blockquote-footer text-white">User One</footer>
                            </blockquote>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-lg-4">
                            <blockquote class="blockquote text-white">
                                <p>"The projects are very practical and useful."</p>
                                <footer class="blockquote-footer text-white">User Two</footer>
                            </blockquote>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-lg-4">
                            <blockquote class="blockquote text-white">
                                <p>"I love the community and support."</p>
                                <footer class="blockquote-footer text-white">User Three</footer>
                            </blockquote>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
            
            <section class="contact py-5">
                <div class="container">
                    <h2 class="fw-bold text-white text-center">Contact Us</h2>
                    <form>
                        <div class="mb-3">
                            <label for="name" class="form-label text-white">Name</label>
                            <input type="text" class="form-control" id="name" placeholder="Your Name">
                        </div>
                        <div class="mb-3">
                            <label for="email" class="form-label text-white">Email</label>
                            <input type="email" class="form-control" id="email" placeholder="Your Email">
                        </div>
                        <div class="mb-3">
                            <label for="message" class="form-label text-white">Message</label>
                            <textarea class="form-control" id="message" rows="3" placeholder="Your Message"></textarea>
                        </div>
                        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Submit</button>
                    </form>
                </div>
            </section>
        </div>
    </div>
